===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|poison|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|potio|pōtio, pōtiōnis|lang=la||drink, a draught, a poisonous draught, a potion}}, from {{term|poto|pōtō|lang=la||to drink}}. See also {{term|potion}} and {{term|potable}}.

