#: ''Suspicion will '''poison''' their relationship.''
#: ''He '''poisoned''' the mood in the room with his non-stop criticism.''
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To cause someone to [[hate]] or to have [[unfair]] [[negative]] [[opinion]]s
